      <gd>THA suas ri bliadhna a nise bhon a choinnich sinn ’nar dithis ann an Glaschu, agus a
        sheulaich sinn ‘Ràitheachan’ Gàidhlig a stéidheachadh.</gd>
      <en>It is up to a year now since the two of us met up in Glasgow, and decided to set up a
        Gaelic ‘quarterly’.</en>
