      <gd>Bha leabhraichean air a bhith ann—bha agus gu leòir dhuibh—ach thàinig fear an déidh fir
        dhiubh gu ìre agus shìolaidh iad air falbh.</gd>
      <en>There have been books–there have and plenty of them–but one after another of them came to
        maturity and they subsided away.</en>
