  <p>
    <s>
      <gd>Ach bha sinn cinnteach as dà nì—gun leugh daoine leabhraichean ma lorgas iad rud-egin
        inntinneach annta, agus cuideachd, mura leugh daoine leabhraichean ’nan cànain fhéin, gun
        téid a’ chànain leis an t-sruth ann an ùine nach bi fada.</gd>
      <en>But we were certain of two things–that peopl will read books if they find something
        interesting in them, and also, if people don’t read books in their own language, that the
        language will go with the tide in a time that is not long.</en>
