    <s>
      <gd>Agus co-dhiùbh, bha agus tha sinn de’n bheachd nach e gnothach a bhuineas do chomhlan beag
        a tha anns a’ Ghàidhlig an diugh, ach gnothach gach mac-màthar a tha a’ gabhail ùidh ann an
        cànain is ann an gnathasan na Gaidhealtachd.</gd>
      <en>And anyway, we were and are of the opinion that Gaelic today is not a matter that belongs
        to a small band, but a matter for every man who takes an interest in the language and
        customs of the Highlands.</en>
      <w id="_400-1-1_d1e1008" ref="agus">Agus</w>
