    <s>
      <gd>Chuir sinn fios a mach thall ’sa bhos, airson cuideachaidh, agus air duilleig eile chì
        sibh mar a ghabh daoine ri ar n-iarrtas, is tha sinn a’ cur tainge chridheil thuca airson an
        cuid fialaidheachd.</gd>
      <en>We have put out information here and there, for help, and on another page you will see how
        people have taken up our request, and we are sending hearty thanks to them for their
        generosity.</en>
      <w id="_400-1-1_d1e1198" ref="cuir" tags="past">Chuir</w>
