    </s>
    <s>
      <gd>Ma chòrdas e ri fear no tè an sud is an so—ma thogas e fiamh gàire is ma dhùisgeas e
        smuain, bithidh sinne riaraichte.</gd>
      <en>If it pleases a man or a woman here and there–if it raises a smile and if it awakens a
        thought, we will be satisfied.</en>
